  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>TAME AND BUILD YOUR TEAM</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your Cosmions, place and combine them to create powerful synergies and beat your opponents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2693940/extras/27fe36368c81d206a03425061fe36141.poster.avif?t=1764297390\" width=592 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2693940/extras/27fe36368c81d206a03425061fe36141.webm?t=1764297390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2693940/extras/27fe36368c81d206a03425061fe36141.mp4?t=1764297390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EVOLVE AND FUSE YOUR COSMIONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Elemental essences to evolve your Cosmions into their advanced forms! Fuse different Cosmions to unlock unique and powerful creations.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2693940/extras/1e16d3535095083abdf13cf66ec9b119.poster.avif?t=1764297390\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2693940/extras/1e16d3535095083abdf13cf66ec9b119.webm?t=1764297390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2693940/extras/1e16d3535095083abdf13cf66ec9b119.mp4?t=1764297390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <strong>BECOME THE ULTIMATE DUELIST!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From your humble neighborhood street to the shiny stadiums of monster battling, win against other players to rise through the leagues, or test your abilities in puzzling Elemental challenges!</p>",
